OL,4,Cfragments of Stone of Destiny after
OL,5,C1951 repair
OL,7,FA search is under way to trace the
OL,8,Fstories of more than 30 fragments of
OL,9,Fthe Stone of Destiny which separated
OL,10,Ffrom the ancient artefact after its
OL,11,Ffamous theft from Westminster Abbey
OL,12,Fand secret repair.
OL,14,FProfessor Sally Foster has been
OL,15,Fpainstakingly collating the history of
OL,16,Fas many of the pieces as possible,
OL,17,Fsome of which were "hidden in plain
OL,18,Fsight", saying they form a fascinating
OL,19,Fnew strand in the centuries-old
OL,20,Fhistory of the Stone of Scone.
