OL,7,FHowever, the exact location of most of
OL,8,Fthese small chips remains a mystery as
OL,9,Fthey have been passed down through
OL,10,Ffamilies or are in private collections.
OL,12,FThis has prompted Prof Foster to
OL,13,Fappeal to anyone who can help her
OL,14,Fresearch to come forward.
OL,16,FMany of the fragments in question came
OL,17,Fabout when a mason secretly repaired
OL,18,Fthe stone after it split in two during
OL,19,Fthe raid by four students in 1950.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
