OL,7,FThis work happened under the
OL,8,Fsupervision of stonemason and
OL,9,Fnationalist politician Bertie Gray,
OL,10,Fwho carefully numbered and recorded
OL,11,Fthe pieces.
OL,13,FHe passed them on to the four students
OL,14,Fwho carried out the heist ` as well as
OL,15,Fthose he admired in and around the
OL,16,Fmovement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
