OL,5,C1951 repair
OL,7,FWhile the existence of fragments from
OL,8,Fthe sandstone block returned in 1951
OL,9,Fhave been known ` an inch-sized piece
OL,10,Fwas gifted to Alex Salmond by Sir Neil
OL,11,FMacCormick and was kept at SNP
OL,12,Fheadquarters ` it has not been widely
OL,13,Fappreciated that there are potentially
OL,14,Fmore than 30 in existence.
OL,16,FProf Foster believes Mr Gray's repair
OL,17,Fwork resulted in as many as 34
OL,18,Fnumbered fragments of the original
OL,19,Fstone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
