OL,7,FThe Commissioners for the Safeguarding
OL,8,Fof the Regalia ` the body of senior
OL,9,Fofficials charged with overseeing the
OL,10,FScottish crown jewels ` are currently
OL,11,Fconsidering what should happen with
OL,12,Fthe fragment gifted to Mr Salmond.
OL,14,FProf Foster's research, funded by the
OL,15,FThe British Academy and the Leverhulme
OL,16,FTrust, has involved combing through
OL,17,Fold newspaper archives dating back
OL,18,Fdecades.
OL,20,FIt has revealed pieces of the stone in
OL,21,Fsome surprising locations.
