OL,7,FFormer lord provost of Glasgow Sir
OL,8,FPatrick Dollan displayed his chip to
OL,9,Fattendees at a concert in 1959.
OL,11,FSpeaking to the PA news agency, Prof
OL,12,FFoster said she met with the
OL,13,Fccommissioners' representatives last
OL,14,Fyear after realising they may be
OL,15,Fmaking a decision about Mr Salmond's
OL,16,Ffragment in "complete ignorance of the
OL,17,Ffact that there were others out there,
OL,18,Fbeyond one that had came to light in
OL,19,F2018".
