OL,7,FShe said: "Even at that stage I was
OL,8,Faware there were other fragments, but
OL,9,FI had not yet realised just many there
OL,10,Fwere going to be.
OL,12,F"There was a case for codifying what
OL,13,Ftheir policy was going to be in
OL,14,Frelation to these, so that people
OL,15,Fwouldn't feel shy about coming forth
OL,16,Fand say they've got ` or had ` a bit
OL,17,Fof it."
