OL,7,FShe continued: "Each one of these
OL,8,Fthings has got a fantastic story in
OL,9,Fits own right, telling us about the
OL,10,Fmeaning of the stone for ordinary as
OL,11,Fwell as famous people.
OL,13,F"Cumulatively, these offer valuable
OL,14,Fnew perspectives to the enduring
OL,15,Frelevance of this national icon."
OL,17,FAs she continued her research project,
OL,18,Ftitled Authenticity's Child, Prof
OL,19,FFoster discovered reports of more and
OL,20,Fmore chips. Some were "hidden in plain
OL,21,Fsight".
