OL,7,FUp until his death in 1975, Mr Gray
OL,8,Fstyled himself as the man who repaired
OL,9,Fthe Stone of Destiny, but he never
OL,10,Fpublicly revealed how many fragments
OL,11,Fhe made.
OL,13,FProf Foster is particularly interested
OL,14,Fin speaking to members of his family
OL,15,Fas they will likely be able to shed
OL,16,Flight on where some of the pieces are.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
