OL,7,FShe is only completely sure about the
OL,8,Flocations of four fragments
OL,9,Fdistributed by Mr Gray, who was
OL,10,Finfluential in the Scottish Covenant
OL,11,FAssociation which pushed for home rule.
OL,13,FWhile the stone itself is a
OL,14,Fparticularly "unprepossessing" item,
OL,15,Fshe argues that understanding the
OL,16,Fstories of these fragments adds a
OL,17,Fpersonal element to its narrative.
