OL,7,FProf Foster said: "It would be lovely
OL,8,Fto see more of these in the public
OL,9,Fdomain and the stories being shared
OL,10,Fand celebrated."
OL,12,FShe has also tracked the fate of
OL,13,Fother, more official, fragments of the
OL,14,FStone of Scone which were taken as
OL,15,Fgeological samples in the 19th century.
OL,17,FThe Stone of Destiny was moved to its
OL,18,Fnew home at Perth Museum last year,
OL,19,Fwhere it sits as the centrepiece of an
OL,20,Fexhibition on Scotland's history.
