OL,7,FWhen Charles was coronated in 2023 it
OL,8,Fwas taken to London where it was
OL,9,Fmounted in the Coronation Chair,
OL,10,Fcontinuing its ancient role in the
OL,11,Fmonarchy.
OL,13,FThe 152kg sandstone block split in two
OL,14,Fduring the famous Christmas Day raid
OL,15,Fof 1950, when four students spirited
OL,16,Fit back to Scotland to try and advance
OL,17,Fthe cause of Scottish independence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
