OL,7,FThe repair work overseen by Mr Gray
OL,8,Finvolved inserting three metal pins to
OL,9,Fhelp join the pieces back together,
OL,10,Fwith a number of chips being created
OL,11,Fas a result.
OL,13,FThe stone was recovered after a few
OL,14,Fmonths when it was left at Arbroath
OL,15,FAbbey and the students who took it
OL,16,Fwere never prosecuted ` they
OL,17,Fmaintained they were simply returning
OL,18,Fthe artefact to Scotland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
